code: export default function validateInfo(values){var errors={};if(!values.firstName.trim()){errors.firstName='First Name is required';}if(!values.lastName.trim()){errors.lastName='Last Name is required';}if(!values.phoneNumber){errors.lastName='Phone Number is required';}if(!values.email){errors.email='Email required';}else if(!/\S+@\S+\.\S+/.test(values.email)){errors.email='Email address is invalid';}if(!values.message){errors.message='Please provide us with some more information.';}return errors;}
